{"tid":2204540,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"點先做到一個專業嘅冗員","createTime":"2020-09-16T06:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T10:39:28.000Z","uid":431,"like":30,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"588ecc80a0b10e366bb37e728cd270697a15a17d","tid":2204540,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:31:54.000Z","msg":"雖然老細畀好多嘢我做，但係我都用盡任何方法偷雞上連登廢噏下<br />\n我仲有無改善空間可以做一個專業冗員？<br />\n<br />\n1) 長期左手放alt+tab上面，訓練到以0.0001秒切換畫面嘅神速<br />\n2) 將個moon較暗少少，等同事經過無咁易睇我個moon顯示乜嘢<br />\n3) browser縮到成個moon嘅1/4，後面開住一個滿載英文嘅word file<br />\n4) 跟足巴打指示，腰板挺直，眼看四面耳聽八方，留意附近有咩風吹草動<br />\n5) 上網用無痕模式，上連登不留痕！<br />\n<br />\n仲有無地方可以改善？我細細個夢想就係做專業冗員，求巴打指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7dfd7db9875e5a38650cf77efe8ca0b04167f5","tid":2204540,"uid":20241,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:32:53.000Z","msg":"台面放啲文件"},{"pid":"c07c644b52d74f1b596d857b31b0447d4ed23f21","tid":2204540,"uid":226092,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:33:29.000Z","msg":"做咁多野都係為左做個冗員<br />\n你都係正正經經返工把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a90fe03288da4b2c9a260183ce491863f2877d","tid":2204540,"uid":205742,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:33:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11dcf48977a554300593698c3c5526856d7bb1d9","tid":2204540,"uid":38891,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:34:15.000Z","msg":"it狗要check一定check得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用手機加數據上網最安全"},{"pid":"57dabe9d8f456b7ca1a5b21e980c80e71ca1ab75","tid":2204540,"uid":32380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:35:13.000Z","msg":"上連登用VPN"},{"pid":"a93dbdc0fa3cf788b66c0a77552e350bfefa1ebb","tid":2204540,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c07c644b52d74f1b596d857b31b0447d4ed23f21","tid":2204540,"uid":226092,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:33:29.000Z","msg":"做咁多野都係為左做個冗員<br />\n你都係正正經經返工把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:35:29.000Z","msg":"你無夢想？"},{"pid":"5e9fa711bbc178ef962dc3d8d97c51f649598f94","tid":2204540,"uid":206617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:36:09.000Z","msg":"WFH<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係公司就去斟多啲水<br />\n公司夠大就四圍行下同人吹進<br />\ncatch up meeting 就不斷問問題，叫老細俾意見<br />\n個 Mon 一係開 doc 一係間 excel <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d6acca673479bac82fdc704202253d108bb370","tid":2204540,"uid":227851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:40:34.000Z","msg":"跟我, 你想點冗都得"},{"pid":"a8d8a4f08170e97383d688233e4afb19081a4c3b","tid":2204540,"uid":327010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d48ee802a12a8f7f04e96475b63963413c478245","tid":2204540,"uid":147770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:44:57.000Z","msg":"女同事瘋狂生仔大肚"},{"pid":"8a4d1a0845ad6c8d833ee96d369cad08cd1c676c","tid":2204540,"uid":9116,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:46:49.000Z","msg":"同你做緊同一樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要睇Youtube睇直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5932f34282d62025cf7ed632ab0444d534b02b97","tid":2204540,"uid":66817,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d50da11203629ed050920a82f6e1856529c12f3","tid":2204540,"uid":128558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:58:52.000Z","msg":"經常去廁所洗手、開大<br />\n去pantry 斟水<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363027adc2013f0f04c45ad61c600bc004ebf274","tid":2204540,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d48ee802a12a8f7f04e96475b63963413c478245","tid":2204540,"uid":147770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:44:57.000Z","msg":"女同事瘋狂生仔大肚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T07:02:13.000Z","msg":"無靚仔同事"},{"pid":"44a27fc76e8e793897abe1eef0cc3f352887aabf","tid":2204540,"uid":282438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T07:34:32.000Z","msg":"邊駛咁麻煩<br />\n每日開工先開個無痕<br />\nLOGIN WHATSAPP、GOOGLE TRANSLATE、GMAIL之類公司用到啲頁面塞落啲分頁到，中間夾個LIHKG<br />\n將個SIZE SET到自己舒服睇<br />\n之後背景就開個WORD/EXCEL<br />\n就可以專心上LIHKG喇<br />\n<br />\n有人黎就轉去WHATSAPP PAGE<br />\n就算轉唔切就轉去TAB去背景個FILE到<br />\n<br />\n啲人問起就話 {要用WHATSAPP WEB 同客溝通又可以打字快又可以攞相，最重要係唔駛成日攞住個電話，等其他人以為我唔做野}"},{"pid":"d487a6b6e62cf28d6398e52b30c8595260db0051","tid":2204540,"uid":266336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T07:34:34.000Z","msg":"返工偷走<br />\n摸熟後，唔返<br />\n但公司無咗你唔得"},{"pid":"a41b667866558b025af1f0113dd8ad74039585f7","tid":2204540,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T07:43:22.000Z","msg":"提防it狗出賣，最基本要整到張枱好亂。"},{"pid":"6e476f75b54150b25e079c95ddf209c779c89532","tid":2204540,"uid":253263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好有建設性 多謝樓子用心分享<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a1dc5d18f6801515a01c8737bfa52e33b28117","tid":2204540,"uid":12492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"363027adc2013f0f04c45ad61c600bc004ebf274","tid":2204540,"ui